-- Asian Development Bank Said Plan Sale of Bonds in Pounds
-- B y   H a n n a h   B e n j a m i n
-- 2012-02-21T10:19:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-21/asian-development-bank-said-plan-sale-of-bonds-in-pounds.html
The  Asian Development Bank  plans to
sell bonds in pounds due December 2015, according to a banker
involved in the transaction.  Credit Suisse Group AG, Deutsche Bank AG and  HSBC Holdings
Plc (HSBA)  are managing the sale, the banker said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Hannah Benjamin in London at 
